I don't have IC handy, but you should just be able to do
a hard cast.
float aFloat = 1.3;
int   anInteger = 0;
anInteger = (int) aFloat; /*cast the float to an int */

/*you can also do it in a function call*/
FuntionTakesAnInt( (int) aFloat );

Hope this helps!
-Chris Prosser




